Simple deterministic 16-character token generator

Endpoints:
- POST /encrypt {"text": "..."} -> {"hash": "16-char-token"}
- POST /decrypt {"text": "...", "hash": "..."} -> {"valid": true/false, "expected": "..."}

Install:
pip3 install -r requirements.txt

Run:
python3 app.py

The token is produced via HMAC-SHA256 using the environment variable HASH_SECRET
or the default 'change_this_secret'. The output uses the requested character set.
